|------|----------------------------------------------------|
| 1    | Create an ECS invoicing method.                    |
| 2    | Choose in a Customer or ECS Setup a Billing Method.|               
| 3    | Run the report Extended Combine Shipments (ECS).   |               
| 4    | View in Sales Invoices the invoices created.       |        